The Renegade (wrestler) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Renegade_(wrestler) 0 Richard Wilson (October 16, 1965 – February 23, 1999) was an American professional wrestler. He was best known for his tenure in World Championship Wrestling (WCW) under the ring name The Renegade, where he was a one-time WCW World Television Champion.
